  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into the exhilarating world of retail with <i>VR Store Simulator</i>!</strong> 🛒 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the ultimate supermarket manager in a stunning VR environment . </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📦 Stock an array of products</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 Satisfy your customers' needs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏪 Master the art of daily store operations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/466f4781f27ba359dca74a469217cdcc.poster.avif?t=1760764409\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/466f4781f27ba359dca74a469217cdcc.webm?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/466f4781f27ba359dca74a469217cdcc.mp4?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your business flourish as you invest in upgrades and expand your store, offering even more to your ever-growing customer base.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/28c8acd72872b747239f53966105ee83.poster.avif?t=1760764409\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/28c8acd72872b747239f53966105ee83.webm?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/28c8acd72872b747239f53966105ee83.mp4?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With incredibly realistic interactions and exciting challenges, <i>VR Store Simulator</i> blends strategic management with immersive fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/07b4d0418b86ea8a6f20d6126b97244b.poster.avif?t=1760764409\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/07b4d0418b86ea8a6f20d6126b97244b.webm?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/07b4d0418b86ea8a6f20d6126b97244b.mp4?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to transform your humble shop into a bustling retail empire?</strong> Jump in and start your journey to success!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into the exhilarating world of retail with <i>VR Store Simulator</i>!</strong> 🛒 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the ultimate supermarket manager in a stunning VR environment . </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📦 Stock an array of products</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 Satisfy your customers' needs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏪 Master the art of daily store operations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/466f4781f27ba359dca74a469217cdcc.poster.avif?t=1760764409\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/466f4781f27ba359dca74a469217cdcc.webm?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/466f4781f27ba359dca74a469217cdcc.mp4?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your business flourish as you invest in upgrades and expand your store, offering even more to your ever-growing customer base.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/28c8acd72872b747239f53966105ee83.poster.avif?t=1760764409\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/28c8acd72872b747239f53966105ee83.webm?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/28c8acd72872b747239f53966105ee83.mp4?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With incredibly realistic interactions and exciting challenges, <i>VR Store Simulator</i> blends strategic management with immersive fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/07b4d0418b86ea8a6f20d6126b97244b.poster.avif?t=1760764409\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/07b4d0418b86ea8a6f20d6126b97244b.webm?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297520/extras/07b4d0418b86ea8a6f20d6126b97244b.mp4?t=1760764409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to transform your humble shop into a bustling retail empire?</strong> Jump in and start your journey to success!</p>",
